    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Sports Journalist - Providing a Single Example\r\n\r\nPractice prompting through the career of a sports journalist by adding a single example to help guide the AI's response.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI for a news summary by including **an example** to help the AI understand what you're looking for. \r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the example affects the tone, structure, or detail in the summary.\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure where to start?**]\r\nHere's an example prompt:\r\n> Summarize the latest sports news as a series of 1-sentence summaries. For example:\r\n>\r\n> Alabama wins over Texas Tech in nailbiter game.\r\n:::",
